<br></li><li>Be fascinated by the simple, but a very exciting story with a twist ending?</li></ul><br>If at least one of your answers is <strong>\"yes\"</strong>, then <strong>this game is for you!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/739190/extras/c0d0b6a404eeb52b6e9786143b0b4a5e.poster.avif?t=1668624177\" width=600 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/739190/extras/c0d0b6a404eeb52b6e9786143b0b4a5e.webm?t=1668624177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/739190/extras/c0d0b6a404eeb52b6e9786143b0b4a5e.mp4?t=1668624177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
